### Criar produto
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Para-brisa Civic 2020",
  "description": "Para-brisa dianteiro Honda Civic 2020",
  "price": 850.00,
  "quantity": 5,
  "category": "Para-brisa"
}

###

### Listar produtos
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar produto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Atualizar produto
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 800.00
}

###

### Desativar produto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
